public class SimilarityNeighborPredicate<O>
extends Object
implements NeighborPredicate<DoubleDBIDList>
    The DBSCAN neighbor predicate for a SimilarityFunction, using all neighbors with a minimum similarity. Reference:

    M. Ester, H.-P. Kriegel, J. Sander, X. Xu
    A Density-Based Algorithm for Discovering Clusters in Large Spatial Databases with Noise
    In Proc. 2nd Int. Conf. on Knowledge Discovery and Data Mining (KDD '96), Portland, OR, 1996.

    Since:
    0.5.0
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
